            "text": "Take the Värmdöleden from Danvikstull, turning towards Saltsjöbaden (Road 228). Pass Tippen and head towards Älgö. After passing Solsidans station, continue onto Älgö. After 4 km, turn onto Berghemsvägen and follow it down to the crag located at the turning point. The last kilometre of Berghemsvägen is closed to unauthorised traffic.",
